個人數係低過上兩次好多嘅話<br />\n<br />\n又會俾人大做文章話民陣個統計有水份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b4f2c4242d48293fcf45dfe2a949935b6e2eb2","tid":1268803,"uid":253106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b89aabe4e4801d589ca3673ebb0d5711a81dc45","tid":1268803,"uid":26637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15649c4a01c0a9d304436aa4ed72ca6c4bd67c05","tid":1268803,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"目前整合<br />\n催淚彈、胡椒噴霧<br />\n[重要] 化學撚教大家應付催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1225082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1225082</a><br />\n發夢夢到幾個德國朋友教我點處理催淚彈 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1</a><br />\n[Gear撚] 催淚彈對防指南 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n裝備<br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立即做兩樣野 購買裝備 同 加強文宣 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1</a><br />\n[突發]新假期繼野餐之後又癡咗線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1</a><br />\n緊急！邊度可以買魔防裝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n盾牌<br />\n[歷史台][積極備盾] 盾牌陣不是亂擺一通的 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1</a><br />\n廉價盾牌材料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1</a><br />\n對付警犬最強盾牌buff <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1</a><br />\n得黑警有盾牌？我都有！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1</a><br />\n盾牌警棍頭盔：反政府示威者裝備不輸警察 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n地形<br />\n【戰棋game】第7-1關佈陣分布圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1266259/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1266259/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n戰術/宏觀部署<br />\n新<br />\n淺 談 顏 色 指 揮 與 組 隊 系 統，又係我隻喪屍GAME<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243970/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243970/page/1</a><br />\n突然!6月30晚立法會煲底集結!不要去灣仔送頭!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265427</a><br />\n----<br />\n《抗爭手語》<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218925</a><br />\n拋磚引玉，大家一齊討論下前線戰術有咩要改善 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1226009/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1226009/page/1</a><br />\n前線有d感想想同香港人講 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218876/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218876/page/1</a><br />\n［純學術討論］漫談「間接路線」軍事理論 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242381/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242381/page/1</a><br />\n高Lv戰士刷副本心得 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241700/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241700/page/1</a><br />\n共產黨起家戰術就係：敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1236578/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1236578/page/1</a><br />\n[為621做好準備] 612檢討大會正式開始討論！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240552/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240552/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n物資<br />\n作為一個物資站站長，我想同大家道個歉 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1</a><br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n鐵馬<br />\n鐵馬一定要放最前！鐵馬一定要有流動性！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1</a><br />\n[人人都要識] 倒三角扎鐵馬 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1</a><br />\n鐵馬最新安置法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\nIT<br />\n[正式上架] 手機抗警犬 用相機Scan數字即出黑警資料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋、漆彈、洗潔精<br />\n漆彈大作戰遊戲攻略 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216185/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216185/page/1</a><br />\n勇武 掉雞蛋好撚on9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242300/page/1</a><br />\n621美食節之如何不令雞蛋發臭 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242159/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242159/page/1</a><br />\n咪撚再講用油/洗潔精/波子 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241029/page/1</a><br />\n記得準備定大量黑色噴漆！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202312/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202312/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8efed0f9d01d7cfbdf09097b7f9f145c67db8c6b","tid":1268803,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3098b70222f9caaca39fd35d65d5c55127c1ad23","tid":1268803,"uid":104957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}